Actually, you'd be surprised.  We always have a couple folks who need flags.  The fact that you can raid with 85% of the raid flagged doesn't mean that you don't need to get everyone flagged.  Issues like folks going LD can cause non-flagged members to be punted from the zone and things like that (yes, we've experienced that).<br>
