<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Doesn't this contradict what the Rotation system is about? Isn't the Rotation system about giving each guild/alliance a chance at specific mobs at certain times when they get onto the rotation of these specific mobs? Giving each guild/alliance an opportunity to take down certain mobs for equipment/questpieces?...<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
