<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Certain Guildleaders have already stated here that they don't have much incentive to do these mobs anymore anyway as they have gotten what they need.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
